<h2>Find a Local Race in Your Community</h2>
<p style="font-size: .9em;">Gather a team of friends or family to participate in a local Turkey Trot or Jingle Bell Jog! Ask for donations per mile logged while helping raise funds and awareness for Parkinson's research. (Looking for a larger commitment? Team Fox is now accepting applications for to fill our <a href="https://www.michaeljfox.org/get-involved/core-athletics.html" style="color: orange;"> 2016 race calendar!</a>)</p>
